hNMD7JliK4vmyIEfQm4g&oe=66D99554"}, {"file_name": "s2.png", "id": "1378895472579717", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035448_1378895475913050_60144634370480235_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WMRzdDIMZbUQ7kNvgE5ynw0&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAx6xEHpugAKkKEv2F3uZ39B0QdIe2f1uE4Xn2gyAjuvg&oe=66D99F89"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "CoverImageSafeAreaTemplateLandscape w1.png", "id": "5102717849764104", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974460_5102717853097437_6970775662564564887_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=JhSuDOABCTsQ7kNvgE3O3ex&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAXoNxWcybvCKfgA7d07izGOWCI_XT3n77OBMOKXtP_OA&oe=66D9A198"}, "display_name": "ZOSU Ocean", "keywords": ["Ocean", "water", "fish", "sea", "shark"], "long_description": "ZOSU Ocean:\n- 30 ocean levels to explore, more of a relaxing experience than a game\n- Over 100 sea animals to save, the majority are randomly spawned\n- Over 60 minutes of timed gameplay in scoring mode\n- This is a relaxing game where you are ZOSU the explorer and you are collecting sea creatures to save them from extinction and to score points\n\nControls:\n- Builtin right hand jetpack for movement. Jetpack body movement is set to the direction of your hand.\n- Walking and jumping movement is set to the direction you are looking.\n- Score points by collecting fish and finding randomly spawned treasure.\n\nGameplay:\n- Timed scoring mode, 2 minutes per level with over 60 minutes of gameplay\n- Freeplay mode, no timer and no scoring\n- This is intended to be a relaxing game and there is no way to take damage or die\n- Sea creatures include starfish, dinosaurs, sharks, squid, many many common and exotic fish, and large sea mammals\n- Bonus island land lobby with climbing and level selection lobby", "short_description": "ZOSU Ocean:\n- 30 ocean levels to explore, more of a relaxing experience\n- Over 100 animals see to save, the majority are randomly spawned\n- Over 60 minutes of timed gameplay in scoring mode\n- This is a relaxing game where you are ZOSU the explorer and you are collecting sea creatures to save them from extinction and score points\n- Sea creatures include starfish, dinosaur fish, sharks, squid, & many others\n- Controls: built in right hand jetpack for movement, additional classic movement options"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://zosustudios.wixsite.com/website/about", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://zosustudios.wixsite.com/website/about", "publisher_name": "ZOSU Studios LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.zosustudios.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "EXPLORATION", "CASUAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8155314127838519"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031488_1300983944005148_7063657349549443708_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=UnJ5r1roBtQQ7kNvgFiv8wY&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDVXEUcJX6ZhIrIHow7hjWkekAd_fBzA_TJRKPKgo3imQ&oe=66D99FC4"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "ZOSU Ocean", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"context_category": "GAMES", "id": "274332603