l with over 60 minutes of gameplay\n- Freeplay mode, no timer and no scoring\n- This is intended to be a relaxing game and there is no way to take damage or die\n- Sea creatures include starfish, dinosaurs, sharks, squid, many many common and exotic fish, and large sea mammals\n- Bonus island land lobby with climbing and level selection lobby", "short_description": "ZOSU Ocean:\n- 30 ocean levels to explore\n- Over 100 animals sea  to save, the majority are randomly spawned\n- Over 60 minutes of timed gameplay in scoring mode\n- This is a relaxing game where you are ZOSU the explorer and you are collecting sea creatures to save them from extinction and to score points\n- Sea creatures include starfish, dinosaur fish, sharks, squid, & many others\n- Controls: built in right hand jetpack for movement, additional classic movement options\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://zosustudios.wixsite.com/website/about", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://zosustudios.wixsite.com/website/about", "publisher_name": "ZOSU Studios LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.zosustudios.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "EXPLORATION", "CASUAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "684443276159230"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 11, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1407712693236492"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "399096969815974"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1407754690054468"}, {"status": "PU